{"tid":616920,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[熱血戒J] 分享成功秘訣！！包你毒撚都變男神！！","createTime":"2018-04-04T14:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T11:42:10.000Z","uid":127929,"like":59,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"034366cf1e947d82f35616397e288b57d65cdd89","tid":616920,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"我先:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">前期準備</span>:清哂電腦啲污漕野先，一定要徹底del哂所有咸野去，包括所有browser 紀錄，各類seed同bt 軟件，清理完成就係戒丁開始之時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">應急方案</span>:用黎阻止想打JJ既反應:<br />\n1.輕度打j反應:想丁個陣就入聖人mode，抄聖經做耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.中度打j反應:揾野做分散注意力，例同條女出街清下銀包，或做下運動消耗下體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.嚴重打j反應:保持冷靜，飲杯水清理下自己既思路，如有需要可以上黎呢個post揾同路人既成功法則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">相信各位戒丁巴絲都攰啦，下面準備左神秘禮物黎提升大家既士氣，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係大家最鐘意既青筋波呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0aa1b396b545c85b9c4db899e3181719faad2ad","tid":616920,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb78e29a59b89243e2e05b55dbcc6c0a9217da04","tid":616920,"uid":72608,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:15:36.000Z","msg":"岩岩破戒 DAY 0 留名<br />\n今次目標3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry